      "content": "hey quick question. im taking sertraline for my mood but finals week is coming up and i feel super low and drained. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost things naturally since the sertraline is a bit mild. is it okay to take them together? or is there a problem with mixing a supplement like that with my prescription?",
